Package: redactr
Title: Prepare Data for LLM Projects by Anonymizing Sensitive Information
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Brandon", "Farr", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "brandon@orderlyquant.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = ""))
Description: Anonymizes sensitive data in vectors and tibbles to allow safe
    inclusion in LLM workflows. Supports format-preserving code redaction,
    grouping variable substitution with thematic word banks, realistic name
    replacement, and within-column numeric shuffling. Stores redaction
    mappings for consistent application across multiple files.
